OL,3,C'Calamitous' flash floods kill more
OL,4,Cthan 300 people in Afghanistan
OL,6,FFlash flooding killed more than 300
OL,7,Fpeople and destroyed over 1,000 houses
OL,8,Fafter unusually heavy seasonal rains
OL,9,Fin Afghanistan, the U.N. food agency
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FFloods hit the country over the last
OL,13,Ffew weeks, mostly in the northern
OL,14,Fprovince of Baghlan, which saw further
OL,15,Fdeluges on Friday.
