OL,3,C'Calamitous' flash floods kill more
OL,4,Cthan 300 people in Afghanistan
OL,6,FThe World Food Program said it was
OL,7,Fdistributing fortified biscuits to the
OL,8,Fsurvivors, as videos posted on social
OL,9,Fmedia showed dozens of people gathered
OL,10,Fat the hospital in Baghlan looking for
OL,11,Ftheir loved ones.
OL,13,FZabihullah Mujahid, the chief
OL,14,Fspokesman for the Taliban government,
OL,15,Fposted on the social media platform X
OL,16,Fthat "hundreds ... have succumbed to
OL,17,Fthese calamitous floods, while a
OL,18,Fsubstantial number have sustained
OL,19,Finjuries."
