OL,3,C'Calamitous' flash floods kill more
OL,4,Cthan 300 people in Afghanistan
OL,6,FMujahid identified the provinces of
OL,7,FBadakhshan, Baghlan, Ghor and Herat as
OL,8,Fthe worst hit. He added that "the
OL,9,Fextensive devastation" has resulted in
OL,10,F"significant financial losses."
OL,12,FHe said the government had ordered all
OL,13,Favailable resources mobilised to
OL,14,Frescue people, transport the injured
OL,15,Fand recover the dead.
OL,17,FThe deaths follow floods in April
OL,18,Fwhich killed at least 70 people and
OL,19,Fdamaged 2,000 homes.
