OL,3,C'Calamitous' flash floods kill more
OL,4,Cthan 300 people in Afghanistan
OL,6,FAfghanistan is still recovering from a
OL,7,Fstring of earthquakes at the beginning
OL,8,Fof the year as well as severe flooding
OL,9,Fin March.
OL,11,FRichard Bennett, U.N. special
OL,12,Frapporteur on the situation of human
OL,13,Frights in Afghanistan, said on X that
OL,14,Fthe floods are a stark reminder of
OL,15,FAfghanistan's vulnerability to climate
OL,16,Fchange and both immediate aid and long-
OL,17,Fterm planning by the Taliban and
OL,18,Finternational actors are needed.
